Greek Ferronickel Producer Larco Returns to Profit, ANA Says

-- B y   P a u l   T u g w e l l
-- 
2011-06-08T13:55:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/greek-ferronickel-producer-larco-returns-to-profit-ana-says.html
Larco SA ,  Europe ’s largest
ferronickel producer, posted a pretax profit last year of 6.4
million euros ($9.4 million) after the price of nickel soared,
the state-run Athens News Agency reported today, citing a Larco
financial statement.  The company reported a pretax loss of 105.5 million euros
in 2009, ANA said.  Greece ’s government plans to sell its 55 percent stake in
Larco during the fourth quarter as part of a program to raise 50
billion euros by the end of 2015 from state asset sales.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Paul Tugwell at 
 ptugwell1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net . 